Text.SourceString: This dark slime... it came from above, the realm of the land-dwellers.
Text.LocalizedString: This dark slime... it came from above, the realm of the land-dwellers.

Text.SourceString: This dark slime... it's a scourge upon our kingdom, rivaling the War of the Seven Kingdoms.
Text.LocalizedString: This dark slime... it's a scourge upon our kingdom, rivaling the War of the Seven Kingdoms.

Text.SourceString: Our kingdom's beauty, its vibrancy... the dark slime threatens to swallow it all. I cannot... will not let that happen.
Text.LocalizedString: Our kingdom's beauty, its vibrancy... the dark slime threatens to swallow it all. I cannot... will not let that happen.

Text.SourceString: Our kingdom has the finest pearls, unparalleled by anything you land-dwellers possess.
Text.LocalizedString: Our kingdom has the finest pearls, unparalleled by anything you land-dwellers possess.

Text.SourceString: This castle has withstood many tides and tempests. It shall not falter to the whims of an outsider.
Text.LocalizedString: This castle has withstood many tides and tempests. It shall not falter to the whims of an outsider.

Text.SourceString: You are a guest here. A guest with strict boundaries. Don't forget that.
Text.LocalizedString: You are a guest here. A guest with strict boundaries. Don't forget that.

Text.SourceString: Your presence here is a privilege. Do not overstep your bounds with our people.
Text.LocalizedString: Your presence here is a privilege. Do not overstep your bounds with our people.

Text.SourceString: Remember, land-dweller, you are only permitted to interact with a select few of us.
Text.LocalizedString: Remember, land-dweller, you are only permitted to interact with a select few of us.

Text.SourceString: Our people are not accustomed to your kind. Tread lightly and only speak when spoken to.
Text.LocalizedString: Our people are not accustomed to your kind. Tread lightly and only speak when spoken to.

Text.SourceString: This 'help' you offer, it's not without strings, is it? Be careful, land-dweller.
Text.LocalizedString: This 'help' you offer, it's not without strings, is it? Be careful, land-dweller.

Text.SourceString: I bear the weight of my people's safety. My concern is not personal, it's my duty. Fables have taught me that your kind has brought both help and harm before.
Text.LocalizedString: I bear the weight of my people's safety. My concern is not personal, it's my duty. Fables have taught me that your kind has brought both help and harm before.

Text.SourceString: Your actions seem to speak of goodwill, but the sea is treacherous, and so too can be the intentions of land-dwellers.
Text.LocalizedString: Your actions seem to speak of goodwill, but the sea is treacherous, and so too can be the intentions of land-dwellers.

Text.SourceString: Our kingdom has always thrived beneath the waves, out of sight of the surface world. Your presence... it stirs unease.
Text.LocalizedString: Our kingdom has always thrived beneath the waves, out of sight of the surface world. Your presence... it stirs unease.

Text.SourceString: Your arrival and the disappearance of my prec-... Our kingdom's relic... a mere coincidence? I find that hard to believe.
Text.LocalizedString: Your arrival and the disappearance of my prec-... Our kingdom's relic... a mere coincidence? I find that hard to believe.

Text.SourceString: Your arrival and the disappearance of our kingdom's relic... a mere coincidence? I find that hard to believe.
Text.LocalizedString: Your arrival and the disappearance of our kingdom's relic... a mere coincidence? I find that hard to believe.

Text.SourceString: You come from the land, an unfamiliar territory to us. Your ways, your intentions, they're as unpredictable as the surface storms.
Text.LocalizedString: You come from the land, an unfamiliar territory to us. Your ways, your intentions, they're as unpredictable as the surface storms.

Text.SourceString: You bear the <NPCName>Goddess</>'s mark, yet she has been silent since... the incident. Peculiar.
Text.LocalizedString: You bear the <NPCName>Goddess</>'s mark, yet she has been silent since... the incident. Peculiar.

Text.SourceString: The <NPCName>Goddess</>... in times of old, her wisdom guided us. But now, in our hour of need, silence...
Text.LocalizedString: The <NPCName>Goddess</>... in times of old, her wisdom guided us. But now, in our hour of need, silence...

Text.SourceString: My sister <NPCName>Liang</> chose the surface, and it swallowed her whole. I worry that you might bring the same fate upon us.
Text.LocalizedString: My sister <NPCName>Liang</> chose the surface, and it swallowed her whole. I worry that you might bring the same fate upon us.

Text.SourceString: Our Colosseum, once strangled by darkness, has been freed. You've done more than I anticipated, land-dweller.
Text.LocalizedString: Our Colosseum, once strangled by darkness, has been freed. You've done more than I anticipated, land-dweller.

Text.SourceString: The sight of <NPCName>Naga</>, free and unbound... It's a sight for weary eyes. Thank you.
Text.LocalizedString: The sight of <NPCName>Naga</>, free and unbound... It's a sight for weary eyes. Thank you.

Text.SourceString: I see... strength returning to our people. Your actions seem to bring about change.
Text.LocalizedString: I see... strength returning to our people. Your actions seem to bring about change.

Text.SourceString: The dark slime... It seems to be receding.//<portrait=normal>A glimmer of hope, perhaps, thanks to you.
Text.LocalizedString: The dark slime... It seems to be receding.//<portrait=normal>A glimmer of hope, perhaps, thanks to you.

Text.SourceString: You've shown yourself capable, but we are not out of the deep sea yet. Stay your course, <PlayerName>$player</>.
Text.LocalizedString: You've shown yourself capable, but we are not out of the deep sea yet. Stay your course, <PlayerName>$player</>.

Text.SourceString: Unless you bring news of progress against the dark slime, spare me your presence.
Text.LocalizedString: Unless you bring news of progress against the dark slime, spare me your presence.

Text.SourceString: Leave, unless you've come with updates on our struggle against the slime.
Text.LocalizedString: Leave, unless you've come with updates on our struggle against the slime.

Text.SourceString: Enough. Be gone.
Text.LocalizedString: Enough. Be gone.

Text.SourceString: I've no time for idle chat. Be gone.
Text.LocalizedString: I've no time for idle chat. Be gone.

Text.SourceString: You've shown courage and determination, land-dweller. The dark slime is gone. We owe you our gratitude.
Text.LocalizedString: You've shown courage and determination, land-dweller. The dark slime is gone. We owe you our gratitude.

Text.SourceString: The sea is clear, the kingdom is safe. This is your doing. I will not forget.
Text.LocalizedString: The sea is clear, the kingdom is safe. This is your doing. I will not forget.

Text.SourceString: A newfound strength flows through our people. You have played a part in this. Thank you.
Text.LocalizedString: A newfound strength flows through our people. You have played a part in this. Thank you.

Text.SourceString: For the first time in a long while, I'm looking forward to tomorrow.
Text.LocalizedString: For the first time in a long while, I'm looking forward to tomorrow.

Text.SourceString: I've noticed a new resolve in our people's eyes. They've found their strength.
Text.LocalizedString: I've noticed a new resolve in our people's eyes. They've found their strength.

Text.SourceString: A weight has been lifted from our shoulders, hasn't it?
Text.LocalizedString: A weight has been lifted from our shoulders, hasn't it?

Text.SourceString: From land-dweller to Merfolk... It seems the sea has accepted you as one of us.
Text.LocalizedString: From land-dweller to Merfolk... It seems the sea has accepted you as one of us.

Text.SourceString: With this new form, you bridge our worlds. It's a responsibility, remember that.
Text.LocalizedString: With this new form, you bridge our worlds. It's a responsibility, remember that.

Text.SourceString: Your transformation... it's remarkable. Could the <NPCName>Oracle</> have intervened in this? It would not surprise me.
Text.LocalizedString: Your transformation... it's remarkable. Could the <NPCName>Oracle</> have intervened in this? It would not surprise me.

Text.SourceString: You are always welcome in our kingdom. As a friend, not a stranger.
Text.LocalizedString: You are always welcome in our kingdom. As a friend, not a stranger.

Text.SourceString: The dark days are behind us. You helped light the way
Text.LocalizedString: The dark days are behind us. You helped light the way

Text.SourceString: Your deeds will be sung by our people for generations to come. You are a friend of our kingdom
Text.LocalizedString: Your deeds will be sung by our people for generations to come. You are a friend of our kingdom

Text.SourceString: Our kingdom is in your debt. You've proven my initial doubts wrong.
Text.LocalizedString: Our kingdom is in your debt. You've proven my initial doubts wrong.

Text.SourceString: The day you arrived, my precious stamina fruit seemed to... vanish. Could it be a simple coincidence?
Text.LocalizedString: The day you arrived, my precious stamina fruit seemed to... vanish. Could it be a simple coincidence?

Text.SourceString: A farmer's life... The rhythm of seasons, the respect for nature... Perhaps it's not too far from our ways beneath the waves.
Text.LocalizedString: A farmer's life... The rhythm of seasons, the respect for nature... Perhaps it's not too far from our ways beneath the waves.

Text.SourceString: You are a surface farmer, yes? That means you till the soil and nurture the land.//It's a humble existence, but one I respect.
Text.LocalizedString: You are a surface farmer, yes? That means you till the soil and nurture the land.//It's a humble existence, but one I respect.

Text.SourceString: Crops nurtured under the sun's warm gaze...//It's a different world from ours, but I can see its allure.
Text.LocalizedString: Crops nurtured under the sun's warm gaze...//It's a different world from ours, but I can see its allure.

Text.SourceString: I'm told there are places on land that rival the beauty of our kingdom. Hard to believe.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm told there are places on land that rival the beauty of our kingdom. Hard to believe.

Text.SourceString: They say there's beauty on land, but can it really match the majestic dance of our kelp forests in the current?
Text.LocalizedString: They say there's beauty on land, but can it really match the majestic dance of our kelp forests in the current?

Text.SourceString: The diversity of our marine life, the sparkle of our pearls...I can hardly imagine the surface surpassing such beauty.
Text.LocalizedString: The diversity of our marine life, the sparkle of our pearls...I can hardly imagine the surface surpassing such beauty.

Text.SourceString: The strength and unity of our people, it's a testament to the kingdom's enduring spirit.
Text.LocalizedString: The strength and unity of our people, it's a testament to the kingdom's enduring spirit.

Text.SourceString: The splendid architecture of our city, it's a symbol of our dedication and craftsmanship.
Text.LocalizedString: The splendid architecture of our city, it's a symbol of our dedication and craftsmanship.

Text.SourceString: The <NPCName>Goddess</> brought you here for a reason. I see that now.
Text.LocalizedString: The <NPCName>Goddess</> brought you here for a reason. I see that now.

Text.SourceString: The throne doesn't come with a manual. One learns by making mistakes, and I've made plenty.
Text.LocalizedString: The throne doesn't come with a manual. One learns by making mistakes, and I've made plenty.

Text.SourceString: As a king, you learn to mask your worries. The people look to you for strength, even when your own wavers.
Text.LocalizedString: As a king, you learn to mask your worries. The people look to you for strength, even when your own wavers.

Text.SourceString: I've always found solace in the company of our sea creatures. Their simple existence, free from burdens of ruling... It's a comforting thought.
Text.LocalizedString: I've always found solace in the company of our sea creatures. Their simple existence, free from burdens of ruling... It's a comforting thought.

Text.SourceString: The songs of the whales... they've changed their tune. It's a melody of hope.
Text.LocalizedString: The songs of the whales... they've changed their tune. It's a melody of hope.

Text.SourceString: When I was a young merling, I used to get lost in the great kelp forests for hours.
Text.LocalizedString: When I was a young merling, I used to get lost in the great kelp forests for hours.

Text.SourceString: There's a legend among us... about a pearl that can grant wishes. Fascinating.
Text.LocalizedString: There's a legend among us... about a pearl that can grant wishes. Fascinating.

Text.SourceString: This necklace belonged to my mother. Each pearl represents a generation that has prospered here, undisturbed. We intend to continue that legacy.
Text.LocalizedString: This necklace belonged to my mother. Each pearl represents a generation that has prospered here, undisturbed. We intend to continue that legacy.

Text.SourceString: Stubborn, they call me. Yet, when it comes to the safety of my kingdom, I prefer steadfast.
Text.LocalizedString: Stubborn, they call me. Yet, when it comes to the safety of my kingdom, I prefer steadfast.

Text.SourceString: When I declined to alter the annual festival's program, many were taken aback.//We honor our past by preserving these ceremonies.
Text.LocalizedString: When I declined to alter the annual festival's program, many were taken aback.//We honor our past by preserving these ceremonies.

Text.SourceString: The royal scribe proposed a new filing system for the archives. Yet, the old one has served us well for generations.//There is no need for change.
Text.LocalizedString: The royal scribe proposed a new filing system for the archives. Yet, the old one has served us well for generations.//There is no need for change.

Text.SourceString: Yes, there are new ideas floating about, but one cannot simply drift with every current.
Text.LocalizedString: Yes, there are new ideas floating about, but one cannot simply drift with every current.

Text.SourceString: It's an old tradition to greet the first sunbeam of the day. Many have forgotten it, yet it warms me to see some still keep it alive.
Text.LocalizedString: It's an old tradition to greet the first sunbeam of the day. Many have forgotten it, yet it warms me to see some still keep it alive.

Text.SourceString: Many of our citizens are pearl collectors. Recently I was gifted with a pearl the size of my fist.//Yes, these fist.
Text.LocalizedString: Many of our citizens are pearl collectors. Recently I was gifted with a pearl the size of my fist.//Yes, these fist.

Text.SourceString: Just yesterday, a young merling asked me why we can't go to the surface. It's difficult to explain our world's boundaries to the innocent.
Text.LocalizedString: Just yesterday, a young merling asked me why we can't go to the surface. It's difficult to explain our world's boundaries to the innocent.

Text.SourceString: When the sun sets, and the Kingdom's lights flicker in the deep blue, I think of each light as one of my people, each deserving of protection and care.
Text.LocalizedString: When the sun sets, and the Kingdom's lights flicker in the deep blue, I think of each light as one of my people, each deserving of protection and care.

Text.SourceString: Today, I had to mediate a feud between two old friends. It's never easy to see harmony disrupted amongst my people.
Text.LocalizedString: Today, I had to mediate a feud between two old friends. It's never easy to see harmony disrupted amongst my people.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Mira</>'s zest for knowledge is insatiable. She reminds me of my younger days.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Mira</>'s zest for knowledge is insatiable. She reminds me of my younger days.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Mira</>'s fascination for your world...it worries me. But her happiness matters above all.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Mira</>'s fascination for your world...it worries me. But her happiness matters above all.

Text.SourceString: I often find <NPCName>Mira</> lost in her dreams, oblivious to the world's harsh realities. I fear the queen and I may have indulged her too much.//<portrait=concerned>It's a world of enchantment for her, without the faintest clue of its true nature.
Text.LocalizedString: I often find <NPCName>Mira</> lost in her dreams, oblivious to the world's harsh realities. I fear the queen and I may have indulged her too much.//<portrait=concerned>It's a world of enchantment for her, without the faintest clue of its true nature.

Text.SourceString: Even as a small merchild, <NPCName>Mira</> was spirited, always seeking out the new and unknown. That curiosity, that boldness... it’s never waned, not for a single tide.
Text.LocalizedString: Even as a small merchild, <NPCName>Mira</> was spirited, always seeking out the new and unknown. That curiosity, that boldness... it’s never waned, not for a single tide.

Text.SourceString: My Queen's wit is sharper than any sea urchin's spine, and just as likely to catch you off guard.
Text.LocalizedString: My Queen's wit is sharper than any sea urchin's spine, and just as likely to catch you off guard.

Text.SourceString: It's thanks to <NPCName>Queen Nanda Devi</> that even in the coldest of winters, our kingdom's tables are never bare.
Text.LocalizedString: It's thanks to <NPCName>Queen Nanda Devi</> that even in the coldest of winters, our kingdom's tables are never bare.

Text.SourceString: My queens blunt remarks used to take me by surprise, but I've come to appreciate their honesty.
Text.LocalizedString: My queens blunt remarks used to take me by surprise, but I've come to appreciate their honesty.

Text.SourceString: The Queen has always had a knack for seeing the potential in every coral reef and kelp forest, and turning it into a bounty for our people.
Text.LocalizedString: The Queen has always had a knack for seeing the potential in every coral reef and kelp forest, and turning it into a bounty for our people.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Liang</>'s fascination for the world above often had her eyes trained upwards, a dreamer yearning for the unknown.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Liang</>'s fascination for the world above often had her eyes trained upwards, a dreamer yearning for the unknown.

Text.SourceString: My sister, <NPCName>Liang</>...//Our juvenile quarrels, though trivial at the time, echo in my mind as joyful banter between siblings.
Text.LocalizedString: My sister, <NPCName>Liang</>...//Our juvenile quarrels, though trivial at the time, echo in my mind as joyful banter between siblings.

Text.SourceString: A week before <NPCName>Liang</> left, she held a prototype of a device, a fusion of human and merfolk technology, with the hope of bridging our two worlds.
Text.LocalizedString: A week before <NPCName>Liang</> left, she held a prototype of a device, a fusion of human and merfolk technology, with the hope of bridging our two worlds.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Liang</> took to the surface without notice, leaving us only with a heartfelt letter.//She vowed to bring back a trove of knowledge, a gift she believed would be a boon for both human and merfolk.//I haven't seen my sister since.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Liang</> took to the surface without notice, leaving us only with a heartfelt letter.//She vowed to bring back a trove of knowledge, a gift she believed would be a boon for both human and merfolk.//I haven't seen my sister since.

Text.SourceString: Few know of this, but en route to Istana, one of the seven Kingdoms, we were once thwarted by an ambush.//<NPCName>Semeru</> made quick work of them. I never had doubts.
Text.LocalizedString: Few know of this, but en route to Istana, one of the seven Kingdoms, we were once thwarted by an ambush.//<NPCName>Semeru</> made quick work of them. I never had doubts.

Text.SourceString: The scar on <NPCName>Semeru</>'s face is not just a remnant of past battles, but a sombering reminder of the threats we face, and the swiftness with which we can lose those we love.
Text.LocalizedString: The scar on <NPCName>Semeru</>'s face is not just a remnant of past battles, but a sombering reminder of the threats we face, and the swiftness with which we can lose those we love.

Text.SourceString: I've tasted delicacies across the seven seas, but <NPCName>Olan</>'s mastery of various cuisines never ceases to amaze me.
Text.LocalizedString: I've tasted delicacies across the seven seas, but <NPCName>Olan</>'s mastery of various cuisines never ceases to amaze me.

Text.SourceString: There was a time when a rare spice was stolen from the kitchen. <NPCName>Olan</>, instead of being upset, improvised and created an even better dish.
Text.LocalizedString: There was a time when a rare spice was stolen from the kitchen. <NPCName>Olan</>, instead of being upset, improvised and created an even better dish.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Miranjani</>'s curiosity reminds me of <NPCName>Liang</>... They both share an intrigue for the surface world.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Miranjani</>'s curiosity reminds me of <NPCName>Liang</>... They both share an intrigue for the surface world.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Mira</>'s fascination with human artifacts... I can't help but think <NPCName>Liang</> would have found it amusing.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Mira</>'s fascination with human artifacts... I can't help but think <NPCName>Liang</> would have found it amusing.

Text.SourceString: I see a reflection of <NPCName>Liang</> in <NPCName>Mira</>'s eyes when she speaks of your world. It fills me with a mixture of dread and nostalgia.
Text.LocalizedString: I see a reflection of <NPCName>Liang</> in <NPCName>Mira</>'s eyes when she speaks of your world. It fills me with a mixture of dread and nostalgia.

Text.SourceString: I encourage <NPCName>Mira</>'s curiosity, yet I can't shake off the painful memories of <NPCName>Liang</>. The surface took her away from us.
Text.LocalizedString: I encourage <NPCName>Mira</>'s curiosity, yet I can't shake off the painful memories of <NPCName>Liang</>. The surface took her away from us.

Text.SourceString: I find satisfaction in the cycle of the day's duty, like the rhythmic dance of the tides.
Text.LocalizedString: I find satisfaction in the cycle of the day's duty, like the rhythmic dance of the tides.

Text.SourceString: The day's duties are numerous, each one requiring a bit of my attention.
Text.LocalizedString: The day's duties are numerous, each one requiring a bit of my attention.

Text.SourceString: The raindrops on the surface are sending a steady pulse through our waters. It's quite serene.
Text.LocalizedString: The raindrops on the surface are sending a steady pulse through our waters. It's quite serene.

Text.SourceString: The winds above have stirred up a lively current today, demanding everyone to stay sharp.
Text.LocalizedString: The winds above have stirred up a lively current today, demanding everyone to stay sharp.

Text.SourceString: The undercurrents are unusually vigorous today, a testament to the powerful winds at the surface.
Text.LocalizedString: The undercurrents are unusually vigorous today, a testament to the powerful winds at the surface.

Text.SourceString: Unless you've brought news of a crisis, allow me to focus on these royal matters.
Text.LocalizedString: Unless you've brought news of a crisis, allow me to focus on these royal matters.

Text.SourceString: I find the quiet comforting after the ordeal. Let's save the talk for another time.
Text.LocalizedString: I find the quiet comforting after the ordeal. Let's save the talk for another time.

Text.SourceString: My work won't finish itself. If there's no emergency, please leave and give me peace.
Text.LocalizedString: My work won't finish itself. If there's no emergency, please leave and give me peace.

Text.SourceString: I've matters to attend to. Leave me, <PlayerName>$player</>.
Text.LocalizedString: I've matters to attend to. Leave me, <PlayerName>$player</>.

Text.SourceString: No need for idle talk, let's enjoy the peace while it lasts.
Text.LocalizedString: No need for idle talk, let's enjoy the peace while it lasts.

Text.SourceString: Your views help connect our world with the land above.
Text.LocalizedString: Your views help connect our world with the land above.

Text.SourceString: It's great to hear from someone who knows both our world and the land above.
Text.LocalizedString: It's great to hear from someone who knows both our world and the land above.

Text.SourceString: Witnessing the Coral Gardens with you has been enlightening.//It's fascinating to see our underwater wonders through your eyes.
Text.LocalizedString: Witnessing the Coral Gardens with you has been enlightening.//It's fascinating to see our underwater wonders through your eyes.

Text.SourceString: I am intrigued by your description of botanical gardens on land. It suggests a shared love for nature's beauty across our realms.
Text.LocalizedString: I am intrigued by your description of botanical gardens on land. It suggests a shared love for nature's beauty across our realms.

Text.SourceString: That evening's dinner with you was more than a meal; it was a cultural exchange, and I am grateful for the experience.
Text.LocalizedString: That evening's dinner with you was more than a meal; it was a cultural exchange, and I am grateful for the experience.

Text.SourceString: Your interactions with our customs, like the use of our oversized fork, have been both amusing and insightful.
Text.LocalizedString: Your interactions with our customs, like the use of our oversized fork, have been both amusing and insightful.

Text.SourceString: Your way of doing things is different, <PlayerName>$player</>.//Very intriguing to witness.
Text.LocalizedString: Your way of doing things is different, <PlayerName>$player</>.//Very intriguing to witness.

Text.SourceString: You've helped me see why it's good for <NPCName>Miranjani</> to learn about both our world and the land. Thank you.
Text.LocalizedString: You've helped me see why it's good for <NPCName>Miranjani</> to learn about both our world and the land. Thank you.

Text.SourceString: It's been good having you around to learn more about the land.
Text.LocalizedString: It's been good having you around to learn more about the land.

Text.SourceString: I always tell <NPCName>Mira</> that a true leader listens as much as they speak, a lesson vital for a future queen.
Text.LocalizedString: I always tell <NPCName>Mira</> that a true leader listens as much as they speak, a lesson vital for a future queen.

Text.SourceString: I taught <NPCName>Mira</> that strength is not just in power, but in showing kindness and understanding to all.
Text.LocalizedString: I taught <NPCName>Mira</> that strength is not just in power, but in showing kindness and understanding to all.

Text.SourceString: One of our most important lessons was about the balance of nature – respecting every creature and plant in our realm.
Text.LocalizedString: One of our most important lessons was about the balance of nature – respecting every creature and plant in our realm.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Miranjani</>'s first swim in the open sea was a proud moment for us. She took to the water like a true mermaid.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Miranjani</>'s first swim in the open sea was a proud moment for us. She took to the water like a true mermaid.

Text.SourceString: As a child, <NPCName>Miranjani</> was fascinated by jellyfish, spending hours watching them pulse through the water.//<portrait=concerned>Those days are long gone; she's into door knobs now.
Text.LocalizedString: As a child, <NPCName>Miranjani</> was fascinated by jellyfish, spending hours watching them pulse through the water.//<portrait=concerned>Those days are long gone; she's into door knobs now.

Text.SourceString: One of my fondest memories is teaching <NPCName>Miranjani</> about the stars above the sea and the creatures below.
Text.LocalizedString: One of my fondest memories is teaching <NPCName>Miranjani</> about the stars above the sea and the creatures below.

Text.SourceString: Nagalita once managed to wrap the entire palace in seaweed during a game of chase, causing quite the spectacle.
Text.LocalizedString: Nagalita once managed to wrap the entire palace in seaweed during a game of chase, causing quite the spectacle.

Text.SourceString: Our royal seahorse, Glint, enjoys sneaking into the treasure vault and playing with the shiny coins.//<portrait=normal><NPCName>Slamet</> takes very good care of them all.
Text.LocalizedString: Our royal seahorse, Glint, enjoys sneaking into the treasure vault and playing with the shiny coins.//<portrait=normal><NPCName>Slamet</> takes very good care of them all.

Text.SourceString: We're very lucky to have him.
Text.LocalizedString: We're very lucky to have him.

Text.SourceString: The tale of the Leviathan, a gentle giant of the deep, has been a bedtime story for mer-children for generations.
Text.LocalizedString: The tale of the Leviathan, a gentle giant of the deep, has been a bedtime story for mer-children for generations.

Text.SourceString: It's concerning to see fewer mer-children in our kingdom these days. The laughter and joy they bring are sorely missed in our waters.
Text.LocalizedString: It's concerning to see fewer mer-children in our kingdom these days. The laughter and joy they bring are sorely missed in our waters.

Text.SourceString: I remember a time when our schools were bustling with young merfolk. It's disheartening to see such emptiness now.
Text.LocalizedString: I remember a time when our schools were bustling with young merfolk. It's disheartening to see such emptiness now.

Text.SourceString: As a king, it troubles me deeply. Our kingdom's future seems uncertain with so few young ones. I often ponder how we might encourage more merfolk families.
Text.LocalizedString: As a king, it troubles me deeply. Our kingdom's future seems uncertain with so few young ones. I often ponder how we might encourage more merfolk families.

Text.SourceString: I'm at a loss, truly. We've tried various initiatives to increase our birth rate, but the results have been disheartening.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm at a loss, truly. We've tried various initiatives to increase our birth rate, but the results have been disheartening.

Text.SourceString: Legends of the Siren's Song, a melody that can calm the fiercest storm, are popular among our people.//<portrait=happy>I've also heard it's well-known among land dwellers. Is that true?
Text.LocalizedString: Legends of the Siren's Song, a melody that can calm the fiercest storm, are popular among our people.//<portrait=happy>I've also heard it's well-known among land dwellers. Is that true?

Text.SourceString: Diplomatic relations with the dolphin pods have been essential in maintaining peace and harmony in our waters.
Text.LocalizedString: Diplomatic relations with the dolphin pods have been essential in maintaining peace and harmony in our waters.

Text.SourceString: Our alliance with the crustacean colonies is vital for keeping an eye on the health of the ocean floor ecosystems.//<portrait=happy>They might just be my favorite underwater communities, if one is allowed to have favorites.
Text.LocalizedString: Our alliance with the crustacean colonies is vital for keeping an eye on the health of the ocean floor ecosystems.//<portrait=happy>They might just be my favorite underwater communities, if one is allowed to have favorites.

Text.SourceString: Merfolk and sea creatures live together in harmony, each respecting the other's role in the ocean.//It's similar to how we cooperate with those on dry land, helping each other out.
Text.LocalizedString: Merfolk and sea creatures live together in harmony, each respecting the other's role in the ocean.//It's similar to how we cooperate with those on dry land, helping each other out.

Text.SourceString: The sunken kingdom of Atlantoria, my ancestral home, holds centuries of our family's history and tales of cohabitation with ancient land dwellers.
Text.LocalizedString: The sunken kingdom of Atlantoria, my ancestral home, holds centuries of our family's history and tales of cohabitation with ancient land dwellers.

Text.SourceString: Our kingdom, known as the 'Sunken Kingdom,' lies deep in the sea near the North Pole. It's not really sunken but hidden from the world above.//<portrait=happy>It's one of the many majestic palaces we own, though I no longer live there.
Text.LocalizedString: Our kingdom, known as the 'Sunken Kingdom,' lies deep in the sea near the North Pole. It's not really sunken but hidden from the world above.//<portrait=happy>It's one of the many majestic palaces we own, though I no longer live there.

Text.SourceString: Growing up in the deeper, colder part of the sea has given me a special appreciation for the stark, serene environment of our polar kingdom.
Text.LocalizedString: Growing up in the deeper, colder part of the sea has given me a special appreciation for the stark, serene environment of our polar kingdom.

Text.SourceString: Our other palace's location, near the North Pole, might seem harsh to some, but the cold depths of the sea there have a majestic and peaceful quality that's unmatched.
Text.LocalizedString: Our other palace's location, near the North Pole, might seem harsh to some, but the cold depths of the sea there have a majestic and peaceful quality that's unmatched.

Text.SourceString: I sent <NPCName>Mira</> there in her younger years to mingle with other merchildren. She seems to prefer warmer waters, however.
Text.LocalizedString: I sent <NPCName>Mira</> there in her younger years to mingle with other merchildren. She seems to prefer warmer waters, however.

Text.SourceString: My father chose this location as the central area of our kingdom, primarily because of its closeness to the land, which helps us maintain stronger ties with surface dwellers.
Text.LocalizedString: My father chose this location as the central area of our kingdom, primarily because of its closeness to the land, which helps us maintain stronger ties with surface dwellers.

Text.SourceString: I spent much of my childhood alternating between here and Atlantoria, learning the intricacies of both underwater realms.
Text.LocalizedString: I spent much of my childhood alternating between here and Atlantoria, learning the intricacies of both underwater realms.

Text.SourceString: Atlantoria wasn't just my home; many royal children, including myself, were raised amidst its ancient halls and deep-sea gardens.
Text.LocalizedString: Atlantoria wasn't just my home; many royal children, including myself, were raised amidst its ancient halls and deep-sea gardens.

Text.SourceString: The Queen, too, spent her early years in Atlantoria, surrounded by its historic splendor, until her teenage years.
Text.LocalizedString: The Queen, too, spent her early years in Atlantoria, surrounded by its historic splendor, until her teenage years.

Text.SourceString: My sibling and I used to race each other to the surface to see who could spot a ship first.//<portrait=concerned>I hope she's well, wherever she is.
Text.LocalizedString: My sibling and I used to race each other to the surface to see who could spot a ship first.//<portrait=concerned>I hope she's well, wherever she is.

Text.SourceString: I'll never forget the first time I saw a whale. It was majestic, gliding through the deep blue like a gentle giant.
Text.LocalizedString: I'll never forget the first time I saw a whale. It was majestic, gliding through the deep blue like a gentle giant.

Text.SourceString: As a kid, <NPCName>Liang</> spent hours watching the surface from below, I should've known.
Text.LocalizedString: As a kid, <NPCName>Liang</> spent hours watching the surface from below, I should've known.

Text.SourceString: Maybe she was right...maybe she belongs up there.
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe she was right...maybe she belongs up there.

Text.SourceString: My sibling and I would race to the surface to spot ships first. Growing up in Atlantoria, it was quite a swim up, and we had to outswim the guards too.//<portrait=happy>I guess <NPCName>Mira</> inherited her rebellious streak from me.
Text.LocalizedString: My sibling and I would race to the surface to spot ships first. Growing up in Atlantoria, it was quite a swim up, and we had to outswim the guards too.//<portrait=happy>I guess <NPCName>Mira</> inherited her rebellious streak from me.

Text.SourceString: My sister and I often sneaked away to the surface to gaze at the stars, she was always curious about the world beyond the sea.
Text.LocalizedString: My sister and I often sneaked away to the surface to gaze at the stars, she was always curious about the world beyond the sea.

Text.SourceString: The Queen and I have known each other since childhood.//<portrait=happy>She's always been a class apart – graceful, wise, and understanding from such a young age.
Text.LocalizedString: The Queen and I have known each other since childhood.//<portrait=happy>She's always been a class apart – graceful, wise, and understanding from such a young age.

Text.SourceString: Our friendship was a constant in the limited circles of royalty; she was, and still is, my closest confidante.
Text.LocalizedString: Our friendship was a constant in the limited circles of royalty; she was, and still is, my closest confidante.

Text.SourceString: Even when we were kids, the Queen had this certain elegance about her.//I suppose you could say I had a crush on her, as land dwellers might put it.
Text.LocalizedString: Even when we were kids, the Queen had this certain elegance about her.//I suppose you could say I had a crush on her, as land dwellers might put it.

Text.SourceString: Making friends was tough for us royals; there weren't many of us, and mingling with commonfolk was off-limits due to security risks.//<portrait=concerned>I hope <NPCName>Mira</> feels less lonely with her two pets, though I know they can't entirely fill that gap.
Text.LocalizedString: Making friends was tough for us royals; there weren't many of us, and mingling with commonfolk was off-limits due to security risks.//<portrait=concerned>I hope <NPCName>Mira</> feels less lonely with her two pets, though I know they can't entirely fill that gap.
